Category:Unidentified Jedi of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: This unidentified Jedi pilot was a male Jedi Knight during the Great Galactic War. He was sent to test drive the Vanguard developed by Rendili Vehicle Corporation on Corellia for the Jedi Order, but he was knocked unconscious and left outside by Hylo Visz when she stole the ship.
